---
title: Marinated Steak Tacos with Charred Pineapple and Lime Crema
description: There are few things more satisfying than steak for dinner. Until now! These carne-loaded tacos are hearty, filling, and most of all—absolutely delicious! Tender bites of tropical-marinated steak are piled into warm tortillas along with charred veggies, tangy lime crema, and juicy pineapple. Taco’bout a weeknight win.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2019-w23-r17-marinated-steak-tacos-bc4fe5c8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/2019-w23-r17-marinated-steak-tacos-5cc216daefe3e40012678a82-d1bcf555.pdf
